text: Confession: I wanted to make a World Music station but I am pretty sure I’d be the only one participating in it.
There’s where I’ve been posting all my spanish party music for now :slightly_smiling_face:
Another Confession: Editing drone footage, and when it ascends over people & looks down on them looking confused it looks like a 90s music video.
If I got 7 people I’d do it, but I figure with so few of us it’d be forgotten pretty quickly.
